#Adipurush #RamSiyaRam 

ADIPURUSH 
CELEBRATING VICTORY OF GOOD OVER EVIL

Gulshan Kumar and T-Series present
A T-Series Films and Retrophiles production 
Starring Prabhas, Saif Ali Khan, Kriti Sanon, Sunny Singh,
Directed by Om Raut.
Produced by Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar, Om Raut, Prasad Sutar, Rajesh Nair

#Adipurush releases IN THEATRES on 16 June 2023 in 3D! 

Watch it in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam.

snippet.title: What If RCB Won the IPL 2023 - MAKE JOKE OF ||MJO|| By Saurabh Shukla
snippet.description:
What If RCB really won the IPL 2023 trophy, presenting another MJO video. Imagining a scenario where the Royal Challengers Bangalore emerges victorious. Watch as RCB fans celebrate in uproarious fashion, with witty jokes, spoofs, and comical situations that will leave you in stitches.

Description link- https://bit.ly/MJOkhiladi 

Video Written, Animated, and Voiced By Saurabh Shukla. 

Keep Loving 
Keep Smiling

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Kya Karie Korimol | ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
snippet.description:
A father-daughter relationship envelops immense compassion, protection, and love. They share a special connection that grows stronger with time and never fades away. #KyaKarieKorimol unveils such a beautiful father-daughter bond on a wedding day. The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single ‚ÄòLike A Sufi‚Äô, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

He‚Äôs accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

Tune in to this masterpiece to get a glimpse of a father-daughter love.

snippet.title: Jhoom Episode 07 Teaser - 27th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Jhoom Episode 07 Teaser - 27th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

A journey of JHOOM into the world of love, relationships, heartbreak, and sacrifice that centers around the lives of two souls who find love in a world of chaos and uncertainty that changes their lives forever. Aryaan is a young and handsome boy who holds a caring and possessive nature towards his friends. Despite having a traumatic past, Aryaan tries to smile through the worries of life and never steps back from helping his friends.

However, Aryaan's life takes an unexpected turn when he meets Maryam, a compassionate and kind-hearted woman who becomes a ray of sunshine in his life. As their relationship begin to flourish, Aryaan feels a change in himself and embraces the love that he had been deprived for so long.

Despite the significant age gap between them, Aryaan and Maryam's love for each other knows no bounds, and they embark on an unconventional journey together. Their love defies societal norms and expectations, challenging the prejudices and biases of those around them.

As their relationship progresses, their love is put to the ultimate test. Will they be able to overcome their challenges and sacrifices to stay together? Will their love stand the test of time and societal pressure? Is age just a number when it comes to love?

Written By: Hashim Nadeem
Directed By: Ali Faizan
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.description:
Venicile Vyapari is a 2011 Indian Malayalam-language Action-romantic comedy film directed by Shafi, starring Mammootty, Kavya Madhavan and Poonam Bajwa . Pavithran, a police constable, has been assigned to investigate the assassination of union leader Ajayan. He disguises himself as a coir merchant to unravel the case .

Ekam gets perplexed after recalling the events surrounding his marriage to Nehmat. He then becomes suspicious and decides to find out the truth with the assistance of Nehmat. Will Ekam be successful this time?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: Harvesting Vegetables from the Garden in Tamil | ‡Æï‡Ææ‡ÆØ‡Øç‡Æï‡Æ±‡Æø ‡ÆÖ‡Æ±‡ØÅ‡Æµ‡Æü‡Øà | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me in our garden for harvesting some vegetables and fruits. We really like growing plants and it is very relaxing. We have some annual vegetables, fruit trees and berry bushes. Alandra also has a lot of fun picking fruits directly from the tree. I highly encourage everybody to try gardening and grow something beautiful. Plants only need light, water, air and patience.

#steffiulagam #steffivlogsintamil #steffigardentour

Friends, hope you will grow some plants at your house too. I wish you all the best and happy gardening!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3782 - 27 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3782: Rishta Aa Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal, or Pyaarelal, receives a phone call from Anjali, who informs him that she has wonderful news concerning his marriage. Pyaarelal hurries to meet Anjali at Gokuldham Society. When he arrives at Anjali's residence, he notices that other Gokuldham females are present. Anjali informs him about her cousin Nanda Kaki, who has a niece named Sapna and is looking for a groom. Pyaarelal is ecstatic after hearing the news and wants to see Sapna and her family right away. Anjali informs Pyaarelal that Sapna and her family will come at 5 in the evening. Pyaarelal now persuades Taarak to attend the gathering, but Taarak informs him that his boss may not grant him an early leave owing to work pressure.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3782, 27 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

snippet.title: PART 2 - RAHUL DUA IN AMERICA | The HORRORS of RENTING a CAR in USA | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua
snippet.description:
"Oh Hello!" Australia and NZ tour (Jun'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour

This video is the 2nd and the most important part of my series of jokes and observations about life in USA. 
These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in just 8 - 9 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. 
Since public transport is nearly absent in USA, I had to rent a car to move around. Though bad, it was the one way. This video is a real life personal account of me renting American Muscle and the horrors associated with it. Via this video I hope to convey all of my anger, surprise, shock, regret and the plethora of other emotions that I felt arising out of the massive inconvenience and hidden charges associated with US Car rental. 
Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #usa #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #carrental #taxes #dodge #americanmuscle #story

Since public transport is nearly absent in USA, I had to rent a car to move around. Though bad, it was the one way. This video is a real life personal account of me renting American Muscle and the horrors associated with it. Via this video I hope to convey all of my anger, surprise, shock, regret and the plethora of other emotions that I felt arising out of the massive inconvenience and hidden charges associated with US Car rental. 
Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #usa #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #carrental #taxes #dodge #americanmuscle #story  

Shot by: Yours Truly & Mehtab Singh 
Edited by Gaurav Bhatt (https://www.instagram.com/gauravbhatt101)

#RaviTeja #Vamsee #AbhishekAgarwal #NupurSanon #GayatriBharadwaj #RenuDesai #MayankSinghaniya #AbhishekAgarwalArts

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamsee‚Äôs Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

GV Prakash Kumar will score muic for the film that has dialogues by Srikanth Vissa. R Madhie ISC will crank the camera and Avinash Kolla is the production designer. Mayank Singhaniya is the co-producer.

snippet.title: Barbie | Main Trailer
snippet.description:
Giant blowout party ‚úÖ
Planned choreography ‚úÖ
New #BarbieTheMovie Trailer ‚úÖ
Only in Theaters July 21.

To live in Barbie Land is to be a perfect being in a perfect place.  Unless you have a full-on existential crisis.  Or you‚Äôre a Ken.

Pre-order/save Barbie The Album: https://barbiethealbum.lnk.to/BTA

From Oscar-nominated writer/director Greta Gerwig (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù) comes ‚ÄúBarbie,‚Äù starring Oscar-nominees Margot Robbie (‚ÄúBombshell,‚Äù ‚ÄúI, Tonya‚Äù) and Ryan Gosling (‚ÄúLa La Land,‚Äù ‚ÄúHalf Nelson‚Äù) as Barbie and Ken, alongside America Ferrera (‚ÄúEnd of Watch,‚Äù the ‚ÄúHow to Train Your Dragon‚Äù films), Kate McKinnon (‚ÄúBombshell,‚Äù ‚ÄúYesterday‚Äù), Issa Rae (‚ÄúThe Photograph,‚Äù ‚ÄúInsecure‚Äù), Rhea Perlman (‚ÄúI‚Äôll See You in My Dreams,‚Äù ‚ÄúMatilda‚Äù), and Will Ferrell (the ‚ÄúAnchorman‚Äù films, ‚ÄúTalladega Nights‚Äù).  The film also stars Michael Cera (‚ÄúScott Pilgrim vs. the World,‚Äù ‚ÄúJuno‚Äù), Ariana Greenblatt (‚ÄúAvengers: Infinity War,‚Äù ‚Äú65‚Äù), Ana Cruz Kayne (‚ÄúLittle Women‚Äù), Emma Mackey (‚ÄúEmily,‚Äù ‚ÄúSex Education‚Äù), Hari Nef (‚ÄúAssassination Nation,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransparent‚Äù), Alexandra Shipp (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù films), Kingsley Ben-Adir (‚ÄúOne Night in Miami,‚Äù ‚ÄúPeaky Blinders‚Äù), Simu Liu (‚ÄúShang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù), Ncuti Gatwa (‚ÄúSex Education‚Äù), Scott Evans (‚ÄúGrace and Frankie‚Äù), Jamie Demetriou (‚ÄúCruella‚Äù), Connor Swindells (‚ÄúSex Education,‚Äù ‚ÄúEmma.‚Äù), Sharon Rooney (‚ÄúDumbo,‚Äù ‚ÄúJerk‚Äù), Nicola Coughlan (‚ÄúBridgerton,‚Äù ‚ÄúDerry Girls‚Äù), Ritu Arya (‚ÄúThe Umbrella Academy‚Äù), Grammy Award-winning singer/songwriter Dua Lipa and Oscar-winner Helen Mirren (‚ÄúThe Queen‚Äù).

Gerwig directed ‚ÄúBarbie‚Äù from a screenplay by Gerwig & Oscar nominee Noah Baumbach (‚ÄúMarriage Story,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Squid and the Whale‚Äù), based on Barbie by Mattel.  The film‚Äôs producers are Oscar nominee David Heyman (‚ÄúMarriage Story,‚Äù ‚ÄúGravity‚Äù), Robbie, Tom Ackerley and Robbie Brenner, with Gerwig, Baumbach, Ynon Kreiz, Richard Dickson, Michael Sharp, Josey McNamara, Courtenay Valenti, Toby Emmerich and Cate Adams serving as executive producers.

Gerwig‚Äôs creative team behind the camera included Oscar-nominated director of photography Rodrigo Prieto (‚ÄúThe Irishman,‚Äù ‚ÄúSilence,‚Äù ‚ÄúBrokeback Mountain‚Äù), six-time Oscar-nominated production designer Sarah Greenwood (‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù), editor Nick Houy (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù), Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù), visual effects supervisor Glen Pratt (‚ÄúPaddington 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù) and music supervisor George Drakoulias (‚ÄúWhite Noise,‚Äù ‚ÄúMarriage Story‚Äù), with music by Oscar winners Mark Ronson and Andrew Wyatt (‚ÄúA Star Is Born‚Äù).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents a Heyday Films Production, a LuckyChap Entertainment Production, a NB/GG Pictures Production, a Mattel Production, ‚ÄúBarbie.‚Äù  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and released in theaters only nationwide on July 21, 2023 and beginning internationally on July 19, 2023.

As Gurugram's white-collar drug-pins share a shaky new normal at a post-covid party apocalypse, Sumair will do anything to save the one relationship that truly matters to him, facing off on one fateful night against drug lords, a crime boss, murderous narcs and straight cops, trapped in a kingpin's lair.

Episode 3781: Pyaarelal Ka Purse
--------------------------------------------------------
The editor of Toofan Express gets angry with Pyaarelal because he altered his name from Popatlal to Pyarelal. Later, he wishes Popatlal to make his new name famous and write more articles. Popatlal takes a half day and makes a visit for documentation of his new name. Later, due to Pyaarelal's name, the police became perplexed as Popatlal lost his wallet and the police gets confused with Pyaarelal and Popatlaal. Watch the episode to know more.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. snippet.title: S8E5 | Deepak Chahar | Breakfast with Champions ft Gaurav Kapur |  @skodaindia   ‚Äã
snippet.description:
From being a little kid who enjoyed the simple village life to becoming one of the most expensive picks in an IPL auction, it has been a wonderful, heart-warming journey for Deepak Chahar.
In this episode of ≈†koda presents Breakfast with Champions, Gaurav Kapur chats with Deepak Chahar, who speaks candidly about his formative years, the practice nets his father set up for him, where he would bowl over 500 balls every day to master the art of swing.

He shares anecdotes from his many years under Dhoni‚Äôs captaincy, including being drafted into the IPL on his batting skills and proposing to his girlfriend on the field.

This episode tastes best with a Kesar Kulhad Chai and a spicy Kachori.

snippet.title: The Biggest Secret | Sound of Silence | Sandeep Maheshwari Spirituality
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com
Connect with him at Facebook.com/SandeepMaheshwariPage
Watch his inspirational videos at Youtube.com/SandeepSeminars
Watch his videos on spirituality at Youtube.com/SandeepMaheshwariSpirituality
